==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Go-devil
<hw>Go"-dev"il</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Mach.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>A weight which is dropped into a bore, as of an oil
well, to explode a cartridge previously lowered.</def> <sd>(b)</sd>
<def>A device, as a loosely fitted plug, which is driven through a pipe
by the pressure of the contents behind the plug to clear away
obstructions.</def> <sd>(c)</sd> <def>A rough sled or dray used for
dragging logs, hauling stone, etc.</def> <mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Godfather</ent>⟦br⟧
